---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Ship Breaking & Recycling - Tahin Spare Suppliers" activeNav="services">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="page-hero-content">
      <h1 class="reveal">Ship Breaking & Recycling</h1>
      <p class="reveal">Home / Our Services / Ship Breaking & Recycling</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container service-detail-container">
      <div class="content-side reveal-left">
        <h2>Sustainable Vessel Demolition</h2>
        <p>Located near the world-renowned Chattogram Ship-Breaking Hub, we facilitate the safe and ecological dismantling of end-of-life vessels. We ensure that the demolition process complies with international environmental and safety standards.</p>
        
        <div class="features-list">
          <ul>
            <li>Safe extraction of reusable marine engines and machinery</li>
            <li>Responsible handling of hazardous materials</li>
            <li>Maximized recovery of scrap steel and reusable metals</li>
            <li>Complete documentation and recycling certification</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <p>Through our ship-breaking activities, we source the high-quality used parts that form the core of our reconditioned spare parts inventory.</p>
        
        <a href="/enquiry" class="btn-primary" style="margin-top: 20px;">Contact for Demolition Services</a>
      </div>
      <div class="image-side reveal-right img-zoom">
        <img src="/images/shipbreaking-yard.webp" alt="Ship Breaking & Recycling" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    position: relative;
    height: 350px;
    background: url('/images/hero-bg.webp') center/cover no-repeat;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .page-hero-overlay { position: absolute; inset: 0; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.6); }
  .page-hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 1; color: #fff; }
  .page-hero-content h1 { font-size: 36px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .page-hero-content p { font-size: 14px; color: #ddd; }

  .service-detail-container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
    gap: 50px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .content-side h2 {
    font-size: 28px;
    color: #222;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .content-side p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }
  .features-list ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 25px 0;
  }
  .features-list li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 25px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #444;
  }
  .features-list li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    color: #c0392b;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
  .image-side img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }
  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #c0392b;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 12px 25px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: background 0.3s;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #a93226;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .service-detail-container { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .image-side { order: -1; }
  }
</style>
